      "content": "hey so i was prescribed some antibiotics for this skin infection on my arm like 3 days ago. i've been taking them every morning but honestly the redness and the swelling are basically totally gone now. do i really need to keep taking them for the full 10 days if i already feel 100% better? i dont really like putting unnecessary stuff in my body if i dont have to",
